SUBSTITUTE FOR
SENATE BILL NO. 219
A bill to amend 1974 PA 258, entitled
"Mental health code,"
by amending sections 401, 427, 430, 461, 468, 472a, and 475 (MCL
330.1401, 330.1427, 330.1430, 330.1461, 330.1468, 330.1472a, and
330.1475), sections 401, 461, 468, 472a, and 475 as amended by 2018
PA 593, section 427 as amended by 2016 PA 320, and section 430 as
amended by 1995 PA 290.
THE PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF MICHIGAN ENACT:
